### Government Routes Test File
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_OFFICER_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### DASHBOARD ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get Dashboard Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Recent Reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/dashboard/recent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Urgent Reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/dashboard/urgent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get My Assignments
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/dashboard/my-assignments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### REPORT MANAGEMENT ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### List Government Reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/reports?page=1&limit=20&sortBy=priorityScore&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Report Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/reports/REPORT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Verify Report (Valid)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/gov/reports/REPORT_ID_HERE/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "result": "valid",
  "note": "Laporan telah diverifikasi dan valid",
  "officerNip": "123456789012345678"
}

### Verify Report (Hoax)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/gov/reports/REPORT_ID_HERE/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "result": "hoax",
  "note": "Laporan tidak valid, terindikasi hoax",
  "officerNip": "123456789012345678"
}

### Assign Report to Officer (Admin Only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/gov/reports/REPORT_ID_HERE/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "officerId": "OFFICER_UUID_HERE",
  "picNip": "123456789012345678",
  "estimatedStart": "2026-04-15T08:00:00Z",
  "estimatedEnd": "2026-04-20T17:00:00Z",
  "budgetIdr": 5000000
}

### Update Report Status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/gov/reports/REPORT_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "newStatus": "in_progress",
  "note": "Perbaikan telah dimulai",
  "officerNip": "123456789012345678"
}

### Update Timeline (Admin Only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/gov/reports/REPORT_ID_HERE/timeline
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "estimatedEnd": "2026-04-25T17:00:00Z",
  "budgetIdr": 7500000,
  "officerNip": "123456789012345678"
}

### Update Priority (Admin Only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/gov/reports/REPORT_ID_HERE/priority
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priority": "urgent",
  "note": "Prioritas dinaikkan karena dampak luas",
  "officerNip": "123456789012345678"
}

### Upload Progress Photo
POST {{baseUrl}}/gov/reports/REPORT_ID_HERE/media
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileKey": "reports/REPORT_ID/progress_photo/1713096000000-uuid.jpg",
  "mediaType": "progress_photo"
}

### ============================================
### ANALYTICS ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Get Analytics Overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/overview?period=30
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Analytics Overview (90 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/overview?period=90
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Analytics Overview (365 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/overview?period=365
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Trends
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/trends?period=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Heatmap Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/heatmap?period=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Performance Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/performance?period=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get AI Insights (Admin Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/analytics/insights
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### OFFICER MANAGEMENT ENDPOINTS (Admin Only)
### ============================================

### List Officers
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/officers?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Officer Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/officers/OFFICER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Officer
POST {{baseUrl}}/gov/officers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "officer@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "nip": "123456789012345678",
  "agencyId": "AGENCY_UUID_HERE",
  "role": "officer",
  "phone": "+6281234567890"
}

### Update Officer
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/gov/officers/OFFICER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe Updated",
  "phone": "+6281234567891",
  "isActive": true
}

### Deactivate Officer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/gov/officers/OFFICER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Officer Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/officers/OFFICER_ID_HERE/stats?period=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### EXPORT ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### Export Reports to PDF
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/export/pdf?status=in_progress
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Export Reports to Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/export/excel?status=completed&startDate=2026-04-01T00:00:00Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Export Summary Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/gov/export/summary?period=30d
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
